OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fjumps as family costs rise 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A single person will need #31,300 a    
OL,6, year for a moderate income in          
OL,7, retirement, according to a pensions    
OL,8, industry body.                         
OL,10,FThe rising cost of living and an       
OL,11,Fexpectation to offer financial support 
OL,12,Fto grandchildren had pushed up the     
OL,13,Fincome required by #8,000, it said.    
OL,15,FThe Pensions and Lifetime Savings      
OL,16,FAssociation (PLSA) uses evidence from  
OL,17,Ffocus groups to make the estimates.    
OL,19,FIt is intended as a guide for those    
OL,20,Fplanning their retirement savings.     
